summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of East Aloha Street from North Broadway to Eleventh Avenue et al, in the City of Seattle, by paving same with asphalt under Ordinance No. 18667, creating Local Improvement District No. 1768 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
